{"tid":2315722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再話冇野可以做 儲錢 移民 再接獲釋手足重新生活","createTime":"2020-12-07T11:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T11:10:51.000Z","uid":201604,"like":33,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ce90401ce79a5fb89338225bfd8e1e6348f0346a","tid":2315722,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:10:01.000Z","msg":"黃圈去到外國 再集中資源幫返手足<br />\n怕有人呃錢 就自己參與 睇實啲條數<br />\n確保每一分每一毫都可以提供手足生活所需<br />\n唔好答我冇可能<br />\n我地香港人冇野叻<br />\n最叻就係返工同搵錢<br />\n<br />\n我地冇大台 見步行步咁行左年半<br />\n係時候諗遠少少 為佢地計劃下<br />\n唔少手足還柙左一年都未判<br />\n一定要畀佢地知道 出返黎可以重新開始<br />\n齊上齊落係真係做得到"},{"pid":"b9394ee3ce68f679fa8866ce8ef359757e0257e0","tid":2315722,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c682f03ad47de925b1afdb2e28dfc53571339417","tid":2315722,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9394ee3ce68f679fa8866ce8ef359757e0257e0","tid":2315722,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"推未"},{"pid":"bc77ca5547f23c2f50477bf21f26f715a109e843","tid":2315722,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dbe176c4aee0ce7afbe24b8110535ff6cd94e73","tid":2315722,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"香港人 移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f97167c80501060cdb6d0fbc7e39183d7dcb23","tid":2315722,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5dbe176c4aee0ce7afbe24b8110535ff6cd94e73","tid":2315722,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:16:18.000Z","msg":"香港人 移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T11:16:46.000Z","msg":"移民先至係真攬炒"},{"pid":"ac7a8b0b91d5